\
### Finding 6: Attraction Performance (Query 6)\
\
**Question:** Which attractions drive revenue?\
\
**TOP 5 ATTRACTIONS:**\
| Attraction | Revenue |\
|-----------|---------|\
| Bondi Beach | $119.9M |\
| Sydney Opera House | $118.7M |\
| Blue Mountains | $118.2M |\
| Great Barrier Reef | $112.3M |\
| Melbourne CBD | $112.0M |\
\
**KEY INSIGHT:**\
- Beach attractions = 30.4% of total attraction revenue\
- Beaches dominate visitor preferences\
- Gift shops = 20% of attraction revenue (opportunity)\
\
**BUSINESS RECOMMENDATION:**\
- Promote beach attractions heavily in international marketing\
- Upgrade gift shop experiences\
- Expected impact: **+$35-55M from attraction strategy**\
\
