\
### Finding 7: Return Visitor Loyalty (Query 7)\
\
**Question:** Are visitors coming back?\
\
**RESULTS:**\
| Country | Return Rate |\
|---------|------------|\
| France | 36% |\
| Germany | 36% |\
| UK | 36% |\
| USA | 35% |\
| **China** | **33% (LOWEST!)** |\
\
**KEY INSIGHT - CRITICAL FINDING:**\
- China #1 market (844K visitors) but LOWEST loyalty (33%)\
- European countries (36%) are most loyal\
- Gap: 3% \'d7 844K = 25,336 lost repeat visitors/year\
- Lost revenue: $96.9M annually!\
\
**BUSINESS RECOMMENDATION - URGENT:**\
- Develop loyalty program for Chinese tourists\
- Improve service quality to match European standards\
- Expected impact: **+$50-75M from loyalty improvement**\
\
