\
### Finding 8: Regional Performance (Query 8)\
\
**Question:** Which regions perform best/worst?\
\
**RESULTS:**\
| Region | Revenue | Rank |\
|--------|---------|------|\
| Melbourne | $1,559.7M | 1 (Strong) |\
| Brisbane | $1,470.7M | 2 (Premium) |\
| Sydney | $1,327.6M | 3 (**CAPITAL CITY PROBLEM!**) |\
| Hobart | $1,212.7M | 8 (Weak) |\
\
**KEY INSIGHT:**\
- Melbourne leads with best experience\
- Sydney (capital) should be #1 but is only 3rd!\
- Sydney visitors stay only 7.4 days (vs 8.3 in other regions)\
\
**BUSINESS RECOMMENDATION:**\
- Learn from Melbourne success model\
- Improve Sydney experience, extend stay length\
- Expected impact: **+$150-200M from fixing Sydney**\
\
