\
### Finding 9: Year-Over-Year Growth (Query 9)\
\
**Question:** Are we growing or declining?\
\
**RESULTS:**\
| Year | Revenue | YoY Growth |\
|------|---------|-----------|\
| 2021 | $557.2M | Baseline |\
| 2022 | $566.6M | +1.69% |\
| 2023 | $583.9M | +3.06% (Best!) |\
| 2024 | $552.8M | **-5.33% (CRISIS!)** |\
\
**CRITICAL INSIGHT:**\
- 2024 revenue DROPPED (worst year in 4 years!)\
- Lost $31.1M compared to 2023\
- Undoes all recovery gains from 2022-2023\
\
**BUSINESS RECOMMENDATION - URGENT:**\
- Investigate root cause of 2024 decline immediately\
- Analyze competitor activity and market shifts\
- Implement recovery plan within 4 weeks\
- Expected impact: **+$30-50M from recovery**\
\
---\
\
### Finding 10: Seasonality by Country (Query 10)\
\
**Question:** Do different countries peak at different times?\
\
**KEY FINDING:**\
- **February Peak (Winter Escape):** China, Japan, USA, France, Germany\
- **January Peak (Holidays):** South Korea, Singapore, Canada, New Zealand\
- **July Peak (School Holidays):** United Kingdom\
\
**BUSINESS RECOMMENDATION:**\
- Run country-specific seasonal campaigns\
- Winter Escape campaign (Nov-Dec) for Northern Hemisphere\
- New Year campaign (Oct-Nov) for holiday markets\
- School Holiday campaign (May-June) for UK\
- Expected impact: **+$90-140M from targeted seasonal campaigns**\
\
---\
\
